messageBody:
I've set up a new Yahoo! group called "Read_Alphabet_Tech".

This group is dedicated to technical discussions of software
development projects related to the Read Alphabet. Topics include
machine transliteration, phonetics, databases, fonts, etc.

I hope many of you will participate.

You can visit the group here: http://groups.yahoo.com/group/read_alphabet_tech

Thanks.

Ted
